Invalid value for option '--platform' (<platforms>): Invalid platform: 'copilot'. Valid values: claude-code, all
Usage: ia-dev-env generate [-fhvV] [--dry-run] [--overwrite-constitution]
                           [-o=<outputDir>] [-s=<stack>] [-p=<platforms>[\s*,
                           \s*<platforms>...]]... [-c=<configPath> | -i]
Generate AI dev environment boilerplate from a YAML configuration or
interactive prompts.
  -c, --config=<configPath>  Path to the YAML configuration file.
      --dry-run              Simulate without writing files.
  -f, --force                Overwrite existing files.
  -h, --help                 Show this help message and exit.
  -i, --interactive          Enable interactive mode.
  -o, --output=<outputDir>   Output directory.
      --overwrite-constitution
                             Regenerate CONSTITUTION.md even if it already
                               exists.
  -p, --platform=<platforms>[\s*,\s*<platforms>...]
                             Target AI platform(s) for artifact generation.
                               Values: claude-code, all. Multiple values
                               separated by comma. Default: all (generate for
                               all platforms).
  -s, --stack=<stack>        Bundled stack profile name.
  -v, --verbose              Enable verbose output.
  -V, --version              Print version information and exit.
